tip.text: Fish and chips is my new favorite here
Staff is extremely inattentive and unwelcoming. But this bacon and mushroom savory brioche bun is nice.
Hoshino has better lava cakes than this

Croque Madam with garlic fries is really good.
Tortilla Espanola: the tomatoes were juicy and great, the combination of capsicum, onion and tomatoes were very good. However, potatoes were too chunky and the bread at the bottom was dry and hard.
Coconut prawns are awesome but there are only three of them
Mutton Vindaloo is great! You can have it with rice or Naan.
My friends highly recommend the char kway teow

Chocolat Fondant with Softee is excellent!
